example.text: From securing derecho relief to making the biggest investment in our infrastructure since the New Deal to lowering prescription drug costs and fighting climate change, we made incredible progress for Iowa families that will continue to deliver well into the future. It has been an honor to represent Iowa's Third Congressional District in Congress, and I am so thankful to have met everyone who participated in my town halls and roundtables, or reached out to my office for help, advice, and resources.
